---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
const lastUpdated = '2024-09-01';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Ermis Consultants & Traders Pvt Ltd (ermisglobal.com). How we collect, use, and protect your personal data."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-neutral-snow">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-neutral-ink mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-muted mb-10">Last updated: {new Date(lastUpdated).toLocaleDateString('en-IN', { day: 'numeric', month: 'long', year: 'numeric' })}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-neutral-ink space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">1. Who We Are</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-muted leading-relaxed">
            Ermis Consultants & Traders Pvt Ltd ("Ermis Global", "we", "our", "us") is a company registered
            in India (CIN: U46590TZ2026OPC038272) operating through the website ermisglobal.com.
            Our registered address is 3/73, Kurundasala Nagar, K. Vadamadurai, NGGO Colony, Kurudampalayam, Coimbatore – 641017, Tamil Nadu, India.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">2. What Data We Collect</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-muted space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li><strong>Enquiry data:</strong> Name, email, phone number, company name, site location, electricity consumption, and messages submitted via our contact and quote forms.</li>
            <li><strong>Newsletter subscriptions:</strong> Email address.</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics data:</strong> Anonymised page views, referral sources, and device types via cookie-based analytics (Google Analytics / Plausible).</li>
            <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, and access logs — retained for security and fraud prevention.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-muted space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li>To respond to enquiries and deliver requested solar assessments or proposals.</li>
            <li>To send newsletters where you have explicitly subscribed.</li>
            <li>To improve our website and services through aggregated analytics.</li>
            <li>To comply with applicable Indian laws, including IT Act 2000 and DPDP Act 2023.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">4. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            We do not sell your personal data. We may share it with:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-neutral-muted space-y-1 text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
            <li>Our CRM and email service providers (HubSpot, etc.) under data processing agreements.</li>
            <li>Netlify (our hosting provider) for form processing.</li>
            <li>Government bodies or regulators where legally required.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Enquiry data is retained for 3 years or until you request deletion.
            Newsletter subscriptions are maintained until you unsubscribe.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            Under applicable Indian data protection law, you have the right to access, correct,
            or request deletion of your personal data. Contact us at
            <a href="mailto:ramc.ermis@gmail.com" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">ramc.ermis@gmail.com</a> for any data requests.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">7. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            We use essential cookies for site functionality and analytics cookies to understand traffic.
            See our <a href="/cookie-policy" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">Cookie Policy</a> for details.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">8. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-muted leading-relaxed text-sm">
            For any privacy-related queries, write to us at
            <a href="mailto:ramc.ermis@gmail.com" class="text-brand-red hover:underline">ramc.ermis@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
